William Henry HOOPER et al., Appellants, v. Kenneth S. THOMSON, Trustee in Bankruptcy of the Estate of Wm. Henry Hooper, Bankrupt, Appellee. No. 6748. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Feb. 15, 1932.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of appellee, ordered appeal dismissed fqr failure, of appellants to file record and .docket pause; mandate forthwith
